  ('locality-6e2f88c7-moex-00028', 'locality-6e2f88c7', 'locality-6e2f88c7-moex-114-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-locality-6e2f88c7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲將其所有A地設定普通地上權於乙，無支付地租之約定。甲復將其所有B地設定10年期限之 普通地上權於丙，有支付地租之約定。甲又將其所有C地設定未定有期限之普通地上權於丁，有 支付地租之約定。依民法規定，下列敘述何者正確？', '["丙得支付未到期之2年分地租後，拋棄其地上權", "丁得支付3年分地租後，拋棄其地上權", "丙拋棄其地上權時，應於1年前通知甲", "乙得隨時拋棄其地上權"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "60d4037cea76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "42e3c5c0be26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "315", "s": "0702", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "法制"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-6e2f88c7-moex-00029', 'locality-6e2f88c7', 'locality-6e2f88c7-moex-114-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-locality-6e2f88c7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲依法受監護宣告。甲受宣告前，並未與他人訂立意定監護契約。法院選定乙任甲之監護人。依 民法關於監護宣告之規定，下列敘述何者正確？', '["乙得以甲之財產購買金融債券、金融機構承兌匯票或保證商業本票", "乙得請求報酬，其數額由甲之親屬會議，按甲之資力酌定之", "乙代理甲購置或處分動產時，非經法院許可，不生效力", "甲之財產，由乙管理。執行監護職務之必要費用，由乙負擔"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "60d4037cea76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "42e3c5c0be26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "315", "s": "0702", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "法制"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-6e2f88c7-moex-00030', 'locality-6e2f88c7', 'locality-6e2f88c7-moex-114-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-locality-6e2f88c7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲男之父為乙。乙之父親為丙。丙之母為丁。丁之妹為戊，戊有一子庚。依民法關於禁止收養親 屬之規定，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["設戊欲收養丙，戊與丙屬禁止收養親屬", "設庚欲收養乙，庚與乙非屬禁止收養親屬", "設庚欲收養甲，庚與甲屬禁止收養親屬", "設丙欲收養庚，丙與庚屬禁止收養親屬"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "60d4037cea76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "42e3c5c0be26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "315", "s": "0702", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "法制"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-6e2f88c7-moex-00031', 'locality-6e2f88c7', 'locality-6e2f88c7-moex-114-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-locality-6e2f88c7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依民法規定，下列關於結婚形式要件之敘述，何者正確？', '["應有公開儀式", "結婚之書面，應當事人親自書寫", "結婚之書面，應經公證", "應由雙方當事人向戶政機關為結婚之登記"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "60d4037cea76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "42e3c5c0be26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "315", "s": "0702", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "法制"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-6e2f88c7-moex-00032', 'locality-6e2f88c7', 'locality-6e2f88c7-moex-114-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-locality-6e2f88c7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲乙為配偶，採分別財產制。乙死亡時，乙與甲之子女丙已死亡。乙尚有外祖父丁、外祖母戊在 世，乙生前均繼續扶養。乙另有祖母庚，與再婚對象辛共同生活。就乙留下之遺產新臺幣（下同） 1,800萬元，戊應可繼承多少？', '["600萬元", "450萬元", "300萬元", "200萬元"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "60d4037cea76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "42e3c5c0be26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "315", "s": "0702", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "法制"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-6e2f88c7-moex-00033', 'locality-6e2f88c7', 'locality-6e2f88c7-moex-114-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-locality-6e2f88c7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於遺囑撤回之敘述，何者錯誤？', '["遺囑人於為遺囑後所為之行為，與遺囑有相牴觸者，其牴觸部分，遺囑視為撤回", "遺囑撤回之方式，為遺囑方式之任何一種均可，但必須與原遺囑同其方式", "撤回前遺囑，且同時另為其他內容之遺囑，亦無不可", "遺囑之撤回，不限於全部，即其一部分亦可"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "60d4037cea76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "42e3c5c0be26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "315", "s": "0702", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "法制"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-6e2f88c7-moex-00034', 'locality-6e2f88c7', 'locality-6e2f88c7-moex-114-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-locality-6e2f88c7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲、乙為夫妻，有丙、丁、戊三子。丙有一子己，丁有一子庚，戊有一子辛。丙先於甲死亡，甲 死亡時，丁依法拋棄繼承。甲之遺產，由何人繼承？', '["乙、戊", "乙、己、戊", "乙、己、庚、戊", "乙、己、庚、辛"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "60d4037cea76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "42e3c5c0be26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "315", "s": "0702", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "法制"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-6e2f88c7-moex-00035', 'locality-6e2f88c7', 'locality-6e2f88c7-moex-114-e6abbdc3', 'sub-locality-6e2f88c7-04', NULL, 'essay', '依行政程序法之規定，法規命令，係指行政機關基於法律授權，對多數
